function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"Implementation of a website-based expert system for COVID-19 diagnosis","Impact":"Misdiagnosis or delayed diagnosis of COVID-19","Mitigation":"Ensure accuracy and reliability of the expert system through thorough testing and validation","Technologies":"Web-based expert system, AI algorithms","People":"Doctors, individuals seeking diagnosis","Owner":"Researchers, developers"},{"Description":"Diagnosis of COVID-19 using CT image features","Impact":"Incorrect diagnosis leading to improper treatment","Mitigation":"Validation of the CT image features and diagnosis results by medical professionals","Technologies":"CT imaging, machine learning algorithms","People":"Doctors, patients","Owner":"Researchers, medical professionals"},{"Description":"Mobile application for COVID-19 symptom diagnosis","Impact":"Inaccurate symptom identification leading to misinformation","Mitigation":"Thorough validation and testing of the expert system rules and symptom indicators","Technologies":"Mobile app, rule-based expert system","People":"General public","Owner":"Developers, health authorities"}]}
